Package com.vectorprint.report.itext.jaxb

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Dataholdingtype
    base type for Java classes holding data, contains information on how to get the data from the Java class, the type of data and style information.
    Datamappingstype
    The configuration consists out of one or more data mapping elements, each describing the mapping to report parts for specific Java classes.
    Datamappingtype
    Each datamappingtype applies to Java classes determined by two attributes, a classname and wether or not the classname is a regular expression.
    Datatypetype
    configuration for types of data (numeric, text, date,...)
    Elementsfromdatatype
    information on how to turn a Java class into multiple elements of the same type
    Elementtype
    information about an iText element to be added for a Java object
    Endcontainertype
    configure the end of a container
    ObjectFactory
    This object contains factory methods for each Java content interface and Java element interface generated in the com.vectorprint.report.itext.jaxb package.
    Startcontainertype
    information about a container to be started and wether or not to add data to it
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Containertypetype
    Java class for containertypetype.
    Elementtypetype
    Java class for elementtypetype.
